Resource Profile: NO Domain VitalSigns Observation - Body Mass Index (BMI)

Defining URL:http://hl7.no/fhir/StructureDefinition/no-domain-vitalsignsobservation-bodymassindex
Version:0.0.1-alpha
Name:NoDomainVitalSignsObservationBodyMassIndex
Title:NO Domain VitalSigns Observation - Body Mass Index (BMI)
Status:Draft as of 5/28/21
Definition:

Base profile for Norwegian Vital Signs Observation Body Mass Index information. Calculated measurement which compares a person's weight and height.

Source Resource:XML / JSON / Turtle

The official URL for this profile is: 

http://hl7.no/fhir/StructureDefinition/no-domain-vitalsignsobservation-bodymassindex
